~ v0.0.3 review-fix verification

~ malformed JSON -> nothing (not a garbage partial)
show json("not json")             ~ nothing
show json("{bad}")                ~ nothing
show json("[1, 2")                ~ nothing  (incomplete)
show json("{} extra")             ~ nothing  (trailing garbage)

~ valid JSON still works
show json("[1, 2, 3]")            ~ [1, 2, 3]
show json("{\"a\": 1, \"b\": [2, 3]}")["b"][1]   ~ 3
show json("[[[[[1]]]]]")          ~ [[[[[1]]]]]

~ surrogate emoji (U+1F600) decodes to ONE codepoint, not two garbage bytes
make e = json("\"\\uD83D\\uDE00\"")
show length(e)                    ~ 1

~ number edge cases
show number("12") + 0             ~ 12
show number("  42  ")             ~ 42
show number("3.5")                ~ 3.5
show number("inf")                ~ nothing
show number("0x1f")               ~ nothing
show number("12abc")              ~ nothing
show number("hello")              ~ nothing
